<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>SplitSheet Studio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="SplitSheet Studio gives music creators a web app and VST workflow for session split capture, signatures, delivery, and rights-ready records.">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="landing-shell">
    <div class="wrap landing-wrap">
      <div class="landing-hero">
        <div class="landing-copy">
          <div class="landing-kicker">SplitSheet Studio</div>
          <h1>Split sheets, signatures, and delivery built for real studio sessions.</h1>
          <p class="landing-subtitle">Capture writer splits, collect signatures, generate final packets, and keep the workflow moving from browser or plugin.</p>
          <div class="landing-actions">
            <a class="landing-button landing-button-primary" href="<%= appUrl %>">Open App</a>
            <a class="landing-button" href="<%= pricingUrl %>">Buy Plugin — <%= pluginPriceLabel %></a>
            <a class="landing-button" href="<%= signupUrl %>">Create Account</a>
            <a class="landing-button" href="<%= blogUrl %>">Read Blog</a>
          </div>
          <p class="landing-note">App host: <strong>app.<%= rootDomain %></strong> · Plugin target: <strong>https://app.<%= rootDomain %></strong></p>
          <% if (!stripeEnabled) { %>
            <p class="small">Payments are not live yet. Accounts, hosted workflow, and plugin testing are live now.</p>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-panel">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>What it does</h3>
            <ul class="landing-list">
              <li>Tracks contributor legal info, roles, shares, and signatures</li>
              <li>Sends invite links or captures in-session signoff</li>
              <li>Generates final PDF packets and stores them durably</li>
              <li>Exposes the same workflow to the web app and VST plugin</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid landing-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Web App</h3>
          <p class="small">Run the full split-sheet workflow in the browser with hosted auth, email delivery, and final packet access.</p>
          <a href="<%= appUrl %>">Go to app</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Account Access</h3>
          <p class="small">Create an account once, then use the same credentials in the browser and plugin. Recovery flows live on the hosted app.</p>
          <a href="<%= signupUrl %>">Sign up</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Plugin Workflow</h3>
          <p class="small">Use the compact studio workflow inside your DAW and point the plugin at the hosted API instead of localhost.</p>
          <a href="<%= pricingUrl %>">Plugin pricing</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Studio Use Case</h3>
          <p class="small">Built for producer and writer sessions where paperwork usually slows down signoff, ownership clarity, and delivery.</p>
          <a href="<%= appUrl %>/split-sheet">Start a split sheet</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card landing-feature-card">
        <div class="landing-feature-header">
          <div>
            <h3>Paid plugin download</h3>
            <p class="small">Sell the VST3 as a direct install while the hosted app handles account sign-in, validation, email delivery, and recovery flows.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="landing-price-lockup">
            <div class="landing-price"><%= pluginPriceLabel %></div>
            <a class="landing-button landing-button-primary" href="<%= pricingUrl %>"><%= stripeEnabled ? "Buy Plugin" : "Join Waitlist" %></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% if (!stripeEnabled) { %>
          <p class="small">Join the launch list at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>?subject=SplitSheet%20Studio%20plugin%20launch"><%= supportEmail %></a>.</p>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="card landing-blog-card">
        <div class="landing-section-header">
          <div>
            <h3>From the blog</h3>
            <p class="small">Rights admin, split-sheet workflow, and sync-readiness notes for artists, producers, and managers.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="<%= blogUrl %>">View all posts</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid landing-grid">
          <% latestPosts.forEach((post) => { %>
            <article class="card landing-post-card">
              <div class="pill"><%= post.category %></div>
              <h3><a href="/blog/<%= post.slug %>"><%= post.title %></a></h3>
              <p class="small"><%= post.excerpt %></p>
              <p class="small"><%= post.publishedAt %> · <%= post.readingMinutes %> min read</p>
            </article>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
